---
title: "Write a post (Producer)"
---
flowchart TD
    A([Producer decides to write a post]) --> B[/Compose text up to 280 characters/]
    B --> C{Text is not empty?}
    C -- No --> B
    C -- Yes --> D[Submit post]
    D --> E{Confirmed as a Producer?}
    E -- No --> F([Rejected — must have Producer role])
    E -- Yes --> G([Post published and visible to followers])
